Achievements.Name: Welcome to Just Dance 2018!
Achievements.Description: Complete your first song.

Achievements.Name: Finding your feet
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on a song.

Achievements.Name: Just Dance Warm-up
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on 5 different songs.

Achievements.Name: NAILED it!
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on a song.

Achievements.Name: Born to Perform
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on 10 different songs.

Achievements.Name: Solid Gold Performance
Achievements.Description: Perform all Gold Moves in a song.

Achievements.Name: You're Gold. GOLD!
Achievements.Description: Perform all Gold Moves in 5 songs.

Achievements.Name: It's all Good!
Achievements.Description: Perform only Good Moves or better in a song.

Achievements.Name: You've got a friend in me....
Achievements.Description: Finish 5 songs with 2 or more players dancing.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Finish!
Achievements.Description: Get a Perfect Move on the last move of a song.

Achievements.Name: Chain Reaction
Achievements.Description: Get 20 or more consecutive Super moves during any song.

Achievements.Name: The perfect combo
Achievements.Description: Get 10 Perfect moves in a row in any song.

Achievements.Name: Out of this world!
Achievements.Description: Get 3 stars on all songs (no Alternate or Kids).

Achievements.Name: The ULTIMATE Just Dance fan
Achievements.Description: Get 5 stars on all songs (no Alternate or Kids).

Achievements.Name: Can you keep a secret?
Achievements.Description: Unlock the gift machine exclusive song.

Achievements.Name: Bronze Age
Achievements.Description: Reach the Bronze rank on all your Dancer Profile stats.

Achievements.Name: Silver Lining
Achievements.Description: Reach the Silver rank on all your Dancer Profile stats.

Achievements.Name: Striking Gold
Achievements.Description: Reach the Gold rank on all your Dancer Profile stats.

Achievements.Name: A long road ahead
Achievements.Description: Reach level 5.

Achievements.Name: What? Already???
Achievements.Description: Reach level 100.

Achievements.Name: Variety Act
Achievements.Description: Dance to every type of song (solos, duets, trios, quartets).

Achievements.Name: Ka-ching!
Achievements.Description: Spend 1000 Mojos in the gift machine.

Achievements.Name: We spared no expense...
Achievements.Description: Spend 10000 Mojos in the gift machine.

Achievements.Name: Gotta Gacha'm all
Achievements.Description: Get all the gift machine rewards.

Achievements.Name: Child's Play
Achievements.Description: Get Rainbow stars 10 times in Kids mode.

Achievements.Name: I got the power!
Achievements.Description: Create a custom Playlist.

Achievements.Name: Who's the boss now?

Achievements.Name: Entering the competition
Achievements.Description: Participate in a Tournament in World Dance Floor.

Achievements.Name: Dream Team
Achievements.Description: Win a Team Battle on the World Dance Floor.

Achievements.Name: Like a rollercoaster!

Achievements.Name: The ride of my life
Achievements.Description: Dance to all Dance Lab episodes.

Achievements.Name: I'm so excited...
Achievements.Description: Reach the "Superstar" rank on all Dance Lab episodes.

Achievements.Name: ...And I just can't hide it!

Achievements.Name: Ready to roll!

Achievements.Name: Risin' up to the challenge
Achievements.Description: Complete 5 challenges.

Achievements.Name: In the Major League
Achievements.Description: Complete 50 challenges.

Achievements.Name: The Comeback
Achievements.Description: Complete one challenge or more per day for 7 days.

Achievements.Name: That's a start!
Achievements.Description: Reach the "Superstar" rank on a song.

Achievements.Name: I woke up like this
Achievements.Description: Reach the "Megastar" rank on a song.

Achievements.Name: Dance Master
Achievements.Description: Reach the "Superstar" rank on all songs (no Alternate versions).

Achievements.Name: Dance Legend
Achievements.Description: Reach the "Megastar" rank on all songs (no Alternate versions).
